HEADWORD: Garment
<hw>Gar"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>garnement</ets>, OF. <ets>garnement</ets>, <ets>garniment</ets>,
fr. <ets>garnir</ets> to garnish. See <er>Garnish</er>.]</ety> <def>Any
article of clothing, as a coat, a gown, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
